high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the granite counter close to the pan and kettle.
Pick up the knife.
Turn around and walk over to the trash can.
Slice up the tomato in the trash can.
Walk to the counter next to the trash can.
Put the knife on the counter.
Walk back over to the trash can.
Take one slice of tomato from the trash can.
Walk over to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the slice of tomato inside. Close the microwave. Turn the microwave on for a few seconds. Turn the microwave off. Open the microwave and take out the slice of tomato.
Walk back over to the trash can.
Put the tomato inside of the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Place a hot slice of tomato inside the trash can.

high_descs: Turn right and go around the corner of the brown island.
Pick the knife up from the brown island that's behind the frying pan.
Turn around and towards the trash can.
Slice the tomato that's in the trash can.
Move right to the brown counter on the left of the stove.
Place the knife on the brown counter to the left of the green cutting board.
Move left to the trash can.
Take a slice of tomato out of the trash can.
Turn left and move move across the room to the microwave on the left.
Cook the slice of tomato on a plate in the microwave and take it back out.
Turn and round and move towards the trash can on the other side of the room.
Put the cooked tomato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a tomato slice that was cooked in the microwave.

high_descs: Go to the other side of the counter.
Pick up the butter knife.
Turn around, walk to the trash can.
Slice the tomato in the trash can.
Take a step to the right.
Put the butter knife next to the fork.
Take a step to the left.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Go to the microwave.
Put the tomato slice in the microwave, heat it up for a few seconds, take the slice of tomato out.
Turn around, go to the trash can.
Throw away the tomato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw away the heated up tomato slice.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step, then turn left and take a step, then turn left to face the table in the center of the kitchen.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn around and step forward to face the trash can.
Cut the tomato in the trash can into slices.
Step to the right and face the counter.
Place the knife on the bottom left corner of the counter.
Step to the left and face the the trash can.
Pick up a slice of tomato from in the trash can.
Turn left and walk across the room, then turn left and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right and walk forward to face the trash can.
Place the tomato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To heat a tomato slice and place it in the trash can.
